    # Observation: citation tool grounding error — product evidence
    narr:Obs_CitationGroundingError a narr:Observation ;
      skos:broader narr:FactualAccuracy ;
      dct:source narr:Sample_CustomerEngManagerVision_20260519 ;
      skos:note "The citation tool, when processing a draft that quoted an engineering manager at the customer's self-description ('I forget as much as I remember'), grounded the quote to the customer's chief architect — because the perspective held the customer's chief architect's version of the sentiment and not an engineering manager at the customer's. The tool reaching for the customer's chief architect is what made the convergence pattern visible. This is a concrete instance of the perspective's coverage gap surfacing through tool behavior: the cite tool correctly found the closest match in the graph, but the closest match was the wrong person. The fix is not a tool fix but a knowledge fix — adding an engineering manager at the customer's self-identification to the perspective." ;
